Ever wondered how some games looked WAY too good for their hardware? I dove deep into 10 "impossible" games that somehow ran on hardware they had no business running on. From Super Mario 3 pushing the NES beyond its limits to Crysis destroying PCs that didn't even exist yet...some of these will blow your mind.
